title: La Caracola
description: A stand in the Atarazanas indoor market in the old part of central Malaga. Enter from the south side (Calle Atarazanas) you will find on your right (puestos 7,8 y 9) an organic-only area with vendors selling fresh fruit and vegetables, nuts and seeds, grains, legumes, tofu, jam, preserves, and other food staples.
